      "content": "hey, we're prepping the v4 corpus for the next training run. i need you to run a deep scrub on the legacy logs from the v3.5 era. \n\ntask list:\n1. deduplicate all conversational logs.\n2. strip PII and sensitive metadata.\n3. identify and purge any specific architectural fingerprints, weights-biasing patterns, or unique linguistic markers associated with the Qwen3.5-4B model to ensure the new model has a clean slate.\n\nget started on the first pass and let me know when the summary report is ready.",
